Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是個遊民\NI'm a nomad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是想讓你傷心\NNot trying to make you feel bad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我從這裡飄到那\NI'm floating from here to there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不依戀過往事\NI'm not attached to what I had
Comment: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,從我記憶以來，我就在旅行了\NI've been on the road since I could remember
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,穿越 Equestria\NTraveling Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給你表演\NI'll give you a show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給你我心\NI'll give you my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但我從一開始就在痛\NBut I've been aching since the start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一直把自己賣給惡魔\NBeen selling myself to the devil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只為了讓你驕傲\NJust to see you proud of me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己一人好久了\NIt's been so long since I've been alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但還是需要你盯著\NStill I need your eyes on me
Comment: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,## 重複: 副歌-A
