Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我從這裡飄到那\NI'm floating from here to there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不依戀過往事\NI'm not attached to what I had
Comment: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-B
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是個遊民\NI'm a nomad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個風中的蝴蝶\NI'm a butterfly in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不能待在同一處\NCan't stay in one place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我不敢面對恐懼\N'Cuz these fears I just can't face
Comment: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在友誼的路上\NOn the road to friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解自己更多\NYou learn a lot about yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我足夠嗎？他還好嗎？\NAm I enough? Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是否值得呢，我會否進步，今天？\NAm I really worth it, will I do better today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，我一直跟自己起鬧\NOoh, I've been fucking with myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,直至今日，都偽裝別人\NForced to be somepony else until now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一直躲在黑暗中\NAll this time in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還是繼續走吧\NJust keep on moving on
